transcript:
Customer: [inaudible] not satisfied [inaudible] pata nahi kaise.
(silence)
Your call has been forwarded.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haanji good morning sir.
Executive: Good morning ma'am. Ma'am wo mera kal connect nahi ho paya tha sir ke sath to abhi kaise connect kar paunga. Mere ko problem jo hai wo resolve karna hai to wo nahi ho pa raha hai.
Customer: Haanji haanji do minute sir mai baat karwati hu aapki.
Executive: Sir aagaye hai.
(silence)
Executive: Hello.
Executive: Hello Naman sir good morning.
Customer: Good morning.
Executive: Sir mai call kar raha tha aapko bhi aap call nahi pick kar pa rahe ho mera.
Customer: Haanji.
Executive: Aah sir mai aap se baat kar raha hu.
Customer: Haanji haanji.
Executive: Sir wo abhi connect kar sakte hai hum log?
Customer: Kya ji karna kya hai?
Executive: Sir aapko jo issues aa raha hai dialing se related usi ke regarding mai bata raha tha kis tarike se aap log feedback wagera share karenge jisse ki hum logo ko pata rahega ki relevancy lead aa rahi hai to kyu aa rahi hai aur small quantities me lead aa rahi hai to sir uske liye bhi mai aapko batata order quantity ko leke to wo sab mere ko guide karna tha aapke sath.
Customer: Mai thodi der me aapko phone karta hu fir karke.
Executive: Kitni der me mai call karu sir aap?
Customer: Ek ghante tak.
Executive: Ek ghante baad.
Customer: Theek hai.

- Customer was unable to connect with executive.

- Wants to resolve the issue.

- Executive offered guidance on dialing issues.

- Executive offered guidance on order quantity.

- Executive will call after one hour.
